{"tid":2054891,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"[ 黨安法的未來 ]  大陸人涉展示毋忘六四標語並拍照上傳微信 以尋釁滋事罪刑事拘留","createTime":"2020-06-07T13:36:27.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-07T16:29:30.000Z","uid":21470,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"70da7d8deab1c0020b88fe187a2dae876285c0c0","tid":2054891,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-07T13:36:27.000Z","msg":"有內地人被拘留 涉展示毋忘六四標語並拍照上傳微信<br />\n2020-06-07 HKT 20:54<br />\n<br />\n湖北人張五洲在日前六四事件31周年當日，在廣州一處街頭出示「勿忘六四、撤回惡法」等標語，並拍照發布到通訊應用程式微信朋友圈及微信群組，他之後被公安以尋釁滋事罪刑事拘留。<br />\n<br />\n根據關注內地維權人士的社交專頁「曉波助瀾會」，張五洲在網上發布有關內容後，清遠市公安在6月5日下午，先以涉嫌擾亂公共秩序為由將他從家中傳喚帶走，24小時後轉為以尋釁滋事罪刑事拘留。而公安今日到張五洲在清遠的家中搜證，公安搜查筆錄上表示，張五洲舉標語拍照傳播的行為屬嚴重破壞社會秩序，但搜查中並無發現涉案相關證據。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1530707-20200607.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1530707-20200607.htm&d=gQ7zj4J1baFceLD6a1UzUiNFMfcMnrnh95DLK%2BYL5kQ%3D&h=c5865fa7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1530707-20200607.htm&h=0aa4aa0c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1530707-20200607.htm</a>"},{"pid":"a3303560f79754128ba6c8ba0bff98aa523f34af","tid":2054891,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-07T16:29:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static02-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/460000/461282/04la7p9_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic02-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F460000%2F461282%2F04la7p9_1024.jpg&h=8b3b7f4c&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}